      "source": [
        "## 7) Drop-in integration notes\n",
        "\n",
        "When you integrate into the real environment:\n",
        "\n",
        "1) Convert env state → `GameState`\n",
        "2) Call the relevant function depending on phase\n",
        "3) Store the returned action back into env\n",
        "\n",
        "Typical mapping:\n",
        "- Discussion phase → `speak(state)`\n",
        "- Voting phase → `vote_on_team(state, proposed_team)`\n",
        "- Mission phase (only if agent on mission) → `mission_action(state)`\n",
        "- Endgame assassination → `assassinate(state)`\n",
        "\n",
        "If you want to evaluate models properly, log:\n",
        "- prompt\n",
        "- raw LLM output\n",
        "- parsed action\n",
        "- final env outcome"
      ]
